MonitorPartialQueue.scala: Implementation of a partial queue using a monitor. 

BoundedMonitorPartialQueue.scala: Implementation of a bounded partial queue
using a monitor.

BoundedPartialQueueTest.scala: Linearizability tester for a partial queue.

SharedSyncChan.scala: a shared synchronous channel. 

SharedSyncChanTest.scala: test for the synchronous channel.

BarberC.scala: sleeping barber example.


